令到個小朋友留下咁大童年陰影，實在可惡！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T22:41:49.000Z","msg":"應該唔止呢個小朋友有童年陰影，隨時成班同學都可能有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7facbcea92edbf63d843b58e181c61903135da7d","tid":2489202,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T22:54:15.000Z","msg":"學校佔好撚重比例責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63ade4e2adeaf62cb0cd4d47ca126eae9881c4e","tid":2489202,"uid":394633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:05:19.000Z","msg":"開老師名未阿，點解仲要係呢間野到讀"},{"pid":"da76bffa7911a728d3cb16650ce27cabce2ced4a","tid":2489202,"uid":157439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"db3c7744dcd7da64870362fdf3334d47816946ed","tid":2489202,"uid":364767,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"bc5b644b85636e544a5b1afa43b77d1c66a3d24b","tid":2489202,"uid":374353,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T20:55:06.000Z","msg":"學校知情不報<br />\n香港防虐兒嘅制度仲好落後"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T22:00:46.000Z","msg":"燒荒荒個呃錢基金<br />\n直到現在都冇表過態"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:22:58.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你唔提起都唔記呢間NGO，真係仆街"},{"pid":"11c506f32138b082039a22c1f4afde16cb9b1268","tid":2489202,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63ade4e2adeaf62cb0cd4d47ca126eae9881c4e","tid":2489202,"uid":394633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:05:19.000Z","msg":"開老師名未阿，點解仲要係呢間野到讀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:34:58.000Z","msg":"老師名就唔知，淨係知間幼稚園叫屯門路德會富泰幼兒園<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1987343/5歲被虐臨臨的幼稚園老師：我真的心碎了?mtc=10016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.l